mbaca-masyarakatnya/attachment/baca2/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca2.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: forums.soompi.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: forums.soompi.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca2-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca2.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43584\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca2.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: forums.soompi.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca2.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca2-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43584\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Goblin. Sumber: forums.soompi.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Gak hanya satu buku aja yang langsung jadi populer. Bahkan semua buku yang berhubungan dengan cerita tentang legenda <i>Goblin, </i>buku anak-anak, sampai ke  penjualan buku mewarnai juga ikut naik dalam peringkat penjualan buku di Korea. Selain drama Goblin, drama Korea yang berjudul <i>‘Because This Is My First Life’</i> juga ikut menggunakan buku puisi romantis dalam dialognya. Buku puisi yang digunakan berjudul <i>‘Island’</i> karya Jeong Hyeong Jong, novel <i>‘To Room 19</i>” karya Doris Lessing, dan <i>“Even If Nothing Change When Crying” </i>karya Park Jun. Semuanya juga laku terjual di toko buku. Kedua drama tadi juga punya rating penonton yang tinggi, sehingga penonton yang menontonnya pun penasaran untuk membacanya juga.</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43586\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43586\" data-attachment-id=\"43586\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/patut-dicontoh-berikut-strategi-korea-untuk-meningkatkan-minat-membaca-masyarakatnya/attachment/baca4/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca4.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: koreandramaland.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: koreandramaland.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca4-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca4.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43586\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca4.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: koreandramaland.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca4.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca4-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43586\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Banyaknya adegan membaca buku di drama korea, meningkatkan minat baca masyarakatnya. Sumber: koreandramaland.com</p></div>\n<div id=\"attachment_43587\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43587\" data-attachment-id=\"43587\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/patut-dicontoh-berikut-strategi-korea-untuk-meningkatkan-minat-membaca-masyarakatnya/attachment/baca5/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca5.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: koreaboo.com\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: koreaboo.com&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca5-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca5.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43587\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca5.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: koreaboo.com\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca5.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca5-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\" /><p id=\"caption-attachment-43587\" class=\"wp-caption-text\">Sumber: koreaboo.com</p></div>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Selain pengaruh dari drama Korea yang bisa meningkatkan minat pembaca, idol di Korea juga ikut punya andil lho. Karena banyak sekali idol yang pergi ke bandara sambil membawa buku di tangannya. Mereka juga suka sharing kepada penggemar tentang buku apa yang sedang dibaca saat ini. Biasanya buku yang dibaca oleh idol kebanyakkan adalah buku puisi atau novel. Penggemar pun jadi ikut penasaran akan apa isi dari buku yang dibaca idolanya.</p>\n<p style=\"text-align: justify;\">Wah, bisa banget, konsep ini diaplikasikan di Indonesia! Memperbanyak film adaptasi novel seperti <i>Dilan</i> misalnya. Siapa tahu kan jadi salah satu cara untuk meningkatkan minat baca anak muda di Indonesia?</p>\n<div id=\"attachment_43585\" style=\"width: 618px\" class=\"wp-caption aligncenter\"><img aria-describedby=\"caption-attachment-43585\" data-attachment-id=\"43585\" data-permalink=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/news/patut-dicontoh-berikut-strategi-korea-untuk-meningkatkan-minat-membaca-masyarakatnya/attachment/baca3/\" data-orig-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca3.jpg\" data-orig-size=\"608,320\" data-comments-opened=\"1\" data-image-meta=\"{&quot;aperture&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;credit&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;camera&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;caption&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;created_timestamp&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;copyright&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;focal_length&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;iso&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;shutter_speed&quot;:&quot;0&quot;,&quot;title&quot;:&quot;&quot;,&quot;orientation&quot;:&quot;1&quot;}\" data-image-title=\"Sumber: raharasi.id\" data-image-description=\"&lt;p&gt;Sumber: raharasi.id&lt;/p&gt;\n\" data-medium-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca3-300x158.jpg\" data-large-file=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca3.jpg\" class=\"size-full wp-image-43585\" src=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca3.jpg\" alt=\"Sumber: raharasi.id\" width=\"608\" height=\"320\" srcset=\"https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca3.jpg 608w, https://ervandra.github.io/ciayoblog/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/baca3-300x158.jpg 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 608px) 100vw, 608px\